#3 Check the possibility to find book - Java Spider
STR
   1. Log in to https://www.yakaboo.ua/
   2. Click on search field
   3. Input text - Java Spider
   4. Click button "Find"
ER
   URL was change
   Check what book with name Java Spider was searched
_____________________________________

#4 Check to add the book to favorite books
STR
   1. Log in to https://www.yakaboo.ua/
   2. Click the My Profile button
   3. Click on Favorite books
   4. Create list
   5. Find book - Java Spider
   6. Click add to favorite
ER
   Book - Java Spider was add to favorite books
   Check what book Java Spider displayed in list of favorite books
_____________________________________

#5 Check the possibility to add the book to cart
STR
   1. Log in to https://www.yakaboo.ua/
   2. Find book - Java Spider
   3. Click on button add to cart
ER
   The book - Java Spider was add to cart
   Check what Java Spider book displayed in cart
